            <title>[FLINK-26118] AsyncSinks do not support downscaling with state</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-26118</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the AsyncSinkWriter assumes to always be restored exactly from only one previous writer state but in case of a downscaling after a snapshot a writer will receive multiple states.&lt;/p&gt;

